short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Count the number of images in the webpage.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This extension is built for SEO Agencies, by SEO agency in Singapore, to identify and count the number of images in the webpage.

The extension will look for images which are defined by the img tag.
